            This is a temporary tool to sync your RingCentral contacts with your AWS contacts. After syncing the contacts books, you will be enable
            to RingCentral Alexa for business making a call by name.</br>
          </p>
          <h2>
            Instructions:
          </h2>
            <ol>
              <li>Login your AWS account and <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/premiumsupport/knowledge-center/create-access-key/">create an IAM access key</a></li>
              <li>Copy the credentials and specify them in the form acordinglly.</li>
              <li>Click the <b>Read Company Contacs</b> button</li>
              <li>From the contacts list, select contacts you want to export to your AWS contacts book</li>
              <li>Click the <b> Export</b> button to export selected contacts</li>
